# Bridge Configuration: torrc-bridge
# This runs a Tor relay in private bridge mode.

# --- Networking ---
ORPort 9001
ExtORPort auto
BridgeRelay 1

# --- Pluggable Transport Settings ---
# This MUST be the absolute path to the compiled 'netshaper-server' executable.
ServerTransportPlugin netshaper exec ./netshaper-bridge -cert-path ./

# The address your PT server will listen on for QUIC connections.
# CHANGED to a high port number (> 1024)
ServerTransportListenAddr netshaper 127.0.0.1:24433

# --- Data and Logging ---
DataDirectory ./tor-bridge-data
Log notice file ./tor-bridge-log.txt
